{"tid":2426804,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：我錯在沒有消毒雙手就把國旗倒轉","createTime":"2021-02-28T10:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T03:45:16.000Z","uid":7439,"like":8,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6092b14dd8b236eac5f82b2e1dd879efa09612d1","tid":2426804,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:43:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U2f2wZalhaE?t=242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU2f2wZalhaE%3Ft%3D242&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3mWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=3e5dc99c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U2f2wZalhaE?t=242</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<em>鄭松泰議員：在侮辱國旗的部分，其實有 5 個類近的元素：焚燒、毀損、塗劃、玷污和踐踏，小弟在《國旗及國徽條例》下所干犯的部分是玷污。我的案件在裁判法院審理，<span class=\"gold\">但我沒有錢上訴，我理應就這 5 點提出上訴。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就玷污這一點而言，與其他數個元素一起來看，其實是頗具體地就着國旗的原形、原狀而定，如果令國旗受到具體侮辱，便會觸犯《國旗及國徽條例》，例如焚燒肯定是，因為是燒毀了；毀損，即扯破了，大家理解嗎？塗劃，即在上面劃了東西；踐踏，即踩在它上面，大家都理解嗎？但是，何謂&quot;玷污&quot;呢？<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">小弟所干犯的玷污，便是因為我的手沒有消毒，然後把國旗倒轉，這便屬玷污。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在《國旗及國徽條例》的實際操作上，有這 5 點作為基本的所謂 indicator(指標)--我說&quot;所謂&quot;，如果這些概念不正確，律師又會指正我--但是，《條例草案》中關於侮辱國歌的罪行可以是&quot;任何方式&quot;，即官方說怎樣便怎樣，大家理解嗎？這是第二個問題。</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/counmtg/floor/cm20200604-confirm-ec.pdf#nameddest=mbp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr19-20%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Ffloor%2Fcm20200604-confirm-ec.pdf%23nameddest%3Dmbp&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3mWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=719e5cbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/counmtg/floor/cm20200604-confirm-ec.pdf#nameddest=mbp</a>"},{"pid":"f13165a49cb35691eeb97694cea1798b606a7fd7","tid":2426804,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:43:25.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰再談基本法：由北京解決，政治死胡同輪不到我去考慮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423002</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0355e9c042d1f887a4e23a1040d7a00803f690fe","tid":2426804,"uid":311626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:43:52.000Z","msg":"泰博<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708620ec3ca444742b4b83577caed988a5ed52d9","tid":2426804,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"鬆太<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5572484e700650d2640b5770f1d56e7c3f66ab23","tid":2426804,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:47:11.000Z","msg":"醒目仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5873f997502ff3b337b353e54424544258d6d70","tid":2426804,"uid":130079,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰是最愛國人士，沒有之一<br />\n<br />\n=========================================<br />\n簽名檔<br />\n<br />\n[戇鳩警報器: 黃世澤 | martin oei | 交加街38號 ] 警世 黃世澤係令大家用唔到BNO移民既始作俑者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423877</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88d15880dbd7a9d57c371c559ffd843d835a89e1","tid":2426804,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:50:07.000Z","msg":"我勁憎熱狗 但今次真係反唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b193b115c8d5e828c025807bcc11d717a609bf","tid":2426804,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88d15880dbd7a9d57